{"tid":10811,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 傑志簽下歐洲球員梅斯達菲","createTime":"2016-11-29T05:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T11:06:15.000Z","uid":8883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b00bcb679f54abdd19045a1080a7b7330c65b8c","tid":10811,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:37:16.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7AJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=59430edf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】傑志周二（11月29日）宣布正式簽入瑞士前鋒梅斯達菲，取代馬高斯的外援名額，這位26歲射手曾效力瑞士U19至U21青年軍，他由2008年起為瑞超球隊巴素利披甲，之後輾轉踢過草蜢及甲組的拉蒙特。梅斯達菲已完成註冊，並可趕及在周六傑志主場對東方龍獅一戰上陣。"},{"pid":"9ecb27b38b6d57e663379ffffeec78632e278b31","tid":10811,"uid":28155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:43:09.000Z","msg":"樓主熱狗"},{"pid":"e0f8c3dbe54b315f45cac6c8702fcadd4b0b2e08","tid":10811,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:45:12.000Z","msg":"雲加又嬴"},{"pid":"626f466f47c2154e0c7995cef78df42ec7978146","tid":10811,"uid":38402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:42:11.000Z","msg":"失業球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f2da02ed7d20b9672ae91bd19b4db6de3e07f0","tid":10811,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:46:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主熱狗</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1190c5c56d48ac45920a6c0f1d6c8518934cc249","tid":10811,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T10:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2823ab0283cb8714999aa9f6ea1173aba9cd8b05","tid":10811,"uid":9305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T10:36:44.000Z","msg":"訓左冇睇 梅斯達菲入左幾多球 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565e